name: "Totem Monsters" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool) & Felicity Echo Hanson
description: [Liner pen and brush pen on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments and color.] This is a collaboration between my toddler granddaughter, Felicity, and me. I drew the original image of the monsters, Felicity added the brush pen colors, and then I digitized and manipulated the whole shebang! ---RFY (HF) & FEH
